            "title": "盤中速報 - 安格(6684)股價拉至漲停，漲停價58.6元，成交934張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>安格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6684:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6684\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6684-TW</a>)16日09:37上漲5.3元，股價漲停報58.6元，委買183,000張，成交934張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為各式多媒體視訊轉換控制晶片及其他控制晶片等研發及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>安格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6684:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6684\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6684-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲10.81%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.34%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-96 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-152 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+56 張</li> <li>融資增減：+31 張</li> <li>融券增減：+15 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
